The job is as follows.\n< Orca >
We have a deal coming up with a certain party.\n< Orca >

Our relationship with them is tense... no, it's
better to say we're adversaries.\n< Orca >

But it's precisely because of that relationship
that the profit from this business is huge.\n< Orca >

Taboo is lucrative, after all. But we can never
let our guard down.\n< Orca >

Both sides are calculating the timing to cut each
other off. Or waiting for the other to make a
move.\n< Orca >

We have to betray them before they betray us. But
the deal is too good. We want to continue it.
Right up to the edge.\n< Orca >

That's where a delicate balance comes into play. A
precarious balance. You get it?\n< Orca >
What should I do?\n< Serena >

You'll act as the intermediary for the deal. No,
I'm not telling you to talk.\n< Orca >

Rather, be silent. Don't speak. Don't do anything
unnecessary.\n< Orca >

During the deal, we'll face them head- on. You'll
step forward from our line, hand over the goods to
them, take the money, and come back. Simple,
right?\n< Orca >

So in the event something happens, I'm the first
one to die, is that it?\n< Serena >

Kukukuku... Don't take it so badly. Your prized
armor should do something, right?\n< Orca >
Perhaps.\n< Serena >
Tch, what an uncharming brat.\n< Orca >
Oh, they've arrived. Do well, okay?\n< Orca >
